n\t\t\t<div id=\"betTbTheadWrap\" class=\"bet-tb-head-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t<table id=\"betTbThead\" class=\"bet-tb bet-tb-dg\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<colgroup>\n                        <col width=\"50\">\n                        <col width=\"70\">\n                        <col width=\"70\">\n                        <col>\n                        <col width=\"50\">\n                        <col width=\"243\">\n                        <col width=\"60\">\n                        <col width=\"81\">\n                        <col width=\"120\">\n                        <col width=\"150\">\n\t\t\t\t\t    <!-- <col width=\"50\"> -->\n\t\t\t\t\t</colgroup>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th class=\"th th-no\">场次</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th class=\"th th-evt\">赛事</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th class=\"th th-endtime\">比赛时间</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th class=\"th th-team\"> <div class=\"team\"> <span class=\"team-l\">主队</span> <i class=\"team-vs\">VS</i> <span class=\"team-r\">客队</span> </div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</th>\n                        <th class=\"th th-bqc\">半全场</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th class=\"th th-betbtn\">\n                            <div class=\"th-betbtn-l\">胜<i>(3)</i></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"th-betbtn-m\">平<i>(1)</i></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"th-betbtn-r\">负<i>(0)</i></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</th>\n                        <th class=\"th th-sbtn\"><span class=\"itm-quanb\">全包</span></th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th class=\"th th-data\">分析</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<th class=\"th th-pei\">\n                            <div class=\"drop2 pei-drop\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"hd\"><span class=\"tit\">百家平均</span> <span class=\"arrow\"></span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bd\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bd-in\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"javascript:;\">平均概率</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"javascript:;\">即时凯利</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"javascript:;\">亚　　盘</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"tips-wrap tips-bjpj\">\n                                <span class=\"ico-help\"></span>\n                                <div class=\"tips-box\" style=\"display: none;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"tips-bd\">\n                                       <dl>\n                                            <dt>百家平均:</dt>\n                                            <dd>“百家平均”是所有公司对一场比赛的胜赔之和除以公司数量，得出“胜”的平均赔率。一般而言，同一场比赛，“百家平均”越低的选项意味着越值得投注。</dd>\n                                            <dt>平均概率:</dt>\n                                            <dd>“平均概率”根据多家公司的平均赔率（指数)换算出的概率，计算对各项打出的可能性的度量。一般而言，平均概率越高，中奖可能性越大，但相应的回报率会更低。</dd>\n                                            <dt>500指数:</dt>\n                                            <dd>“500指数”是500彩票网根据球队实力、投注倾向以及权威博彩公司赔率等数据综合计算得来。一般而言，同一场比赛，“500指数”越高的选项意味着越值得投注。</dd>\n                                            <dt>即时凯利:</dt>\n                                            <dd>“即时凯利”反映各项赔率存在的市场赔付风险，某项的凯利指数高于返还率，则表明该项的市场风险很大，难以打出；反之则市场风险小，容易打出。</dd>\n                                        </dl>\n                                    </div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n                            </div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</th>\n                        <th class=\"th th-usr last\">本站用户投注比例</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<!-- <th class=\"th last th-top\">置顶</th> --> \n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<!-- 表格头 结束 -->\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<table class=\"bet-tb bet-tb-dg\" id=\"vsTable\">\n\t\t\t\t<colgroup>\n                    <col width=\"50\">\n                    <col width=\"70\">\n                    <col width=\"70\">\n                    <col>\n                    <col width=\"50\">\n                    <col width=\"244\">\n                    <col width=\"60\">\n                    <col width=\"80\">\n                    <col width=\"120\">\n                    <col width=\"150\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<!-- <col width=\"50\"> -->\n\t\t\t\t</colgroup>\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\n\t\t\t\t<tr 